&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years’ experience in pricing, analytics, data science, or a related analytical field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Mathematics, Data Science, Business Intelligence, Statistics, Business, or a related field.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with SQL.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to analyze large data sets and translate findings into business recommendations.Ability to communicate data analysis to technical and non-technical stakeholders.Experience developing reports, dashboards, or recurring analytical tools.Knowledge of pricing, profitability, competitive analysis, or related business analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in pricing analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in R, Python, or artificial intelligence tools such as OpenAI, Gemini, or related APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&

