&lt;li&gt;4+ years of project/product delivery experience in Agile environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of Agile delivery methodologies, SDLC, and project management concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agile certification required (CSM, CSPO, PMI-ACP, or equivalent).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced experience with Jira, Confluence, and Microsoft Office Suite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication, facilitation, and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with leveraging AI-powered tools (e.g., for documentation, analysis, or workflow optimization) to enhance team efficiency and delivery outcomes preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PMP certification preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
