&lt;p&gt;Beyond individual category management, this role carries a broader strategic impact by leading strategic and operational initiatives on behalf of the entire Category Management team to drive scalable results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Sr. Category Manager’s success will be defined by unlocking the future portfolio with identification and development of new supplier relationships as well as accelerating the sales of the existing portfolio of products, and delivering executive business reviews for strategic partners..&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
