&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand vertical market segments and demonstrate solid analytical skills to be able to mine data, understand the drivers of your business, and create category strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect, sell, and negotiate contracts with suppliers to achieve a fast launch to market with the highest level of success while managing within operational capabilities and profitability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver executive business reviews for strategic suppliers that define, among other things, supplier performance, product line expansion roadmaps, supplier capabilities, and/or challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the Zoro customer and connect products to customer needs, including understanding new product trends and technologies and differences among brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively lead team members and coach team member(s) to contribute to talent development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional partners to gain buy-in and drive support for key category initiatives

