&lt;li&gt;Content strategy to support product discovery and decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify patterns and opportunities across categories and translate them into scalable strategies and standards&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set team priorities and ensure focus on the highest-impact opportunities for customer experience and business performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Digital Merchandising Global Experience Strategy to align category-level approaches with sitewide systems and influence global defaults&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Category Management, Product, Product Information &amp;amp; Enrichment, Marketing, and Analytics to bring strategies to life&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and oversee testing strategies to validate category-level opportunities and scale what works&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to and influence the Digital Merchandising roadmap in partnership with Experience Strategy and Product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and scale the Category Experience function, including defining roles, responsibilities, and ways of working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish clear goals and performance expectations for the team, aligned to business and customer outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure high-quality, consistent execution of category strategies across the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and reinforce a test-and-learn culture, ensuring continuous improvement across category experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
